14.18
log
@pass bu_exit a NULL instead of an empty string
@
text
@/*                       P I X - P N G . C
 * BRL-CAD
 *
 * Copyright (c) 1998-2007 United States Government as represented by
 * the U.S. Army Research Laboratory.
